snippet.title: Mass Effect 3: Emergency Broadcast Teaser (E3 2011)
snippet.description:
Check out the new story trailer for the game Mass Effect 3. Earth is attacked by the Reapers as the world tries to warn its people in this E3 2011 trailer.

IGN's YouTube is just a taste of our content. Get more:
